The science behind these code and its use is described in a publication submitted to Intrinsically Disordered Proteins journal.
If you use MaxEnt and/or RunPales, please cite this publication (when of if accepted, details will be updated):

Melchor Sanchez-Martinez, Ramon Crehuet 'Applying the Maximum Entropy Principle to determine ensembles of Intrinsically 
Disordered Proteins from Residual Dipolar Couplings', submitted to Phys. Chem. Chem. Phys., 2014
